## Page 2: Guide Detail (`src/app/guide/[guideId]/[slug]/page.tsx`)

### Current Behavior
- First `useEffect`: Fetches guide, comments, and recommendations in parallel
- Second `useEffect`: Checks like/save/follow status when user is available
- Renders: MediaGallery, title/meta, AuthorCard, GuideActions, ChatTimeline, CommentSection, Recommendations

### Target Architecture

**Server Component Structure:**
```
src/app/guide/[guideId]/[slug]/page.tsx (Server Component)
  - Fetches guide data, comments, recommendations
  - Gets current user from server session
  - Passes data to client wrapper

src/app/guide/[guideId]/[slug]/loading.tsx (NEW)
  - Suspense fallback

src/components/guide/guide-detail-client.tsx (NEW Client Component)
  - Handles user-specific status checks (like/save/follow)
